      "id": "e2c89de0-ccc5-4d97-b87d-888b46cb1ae1",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Observed that the square of a number flips a negative number to a positive one.\n\nNow lets sort it. Using stream has the time complexity of O(n log n)",
