    {
      "id": "2effc042-bbe5-4957-8817-4a71a4afeac0",
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Using this steam, we can now with ease get the array sorted with squared values",
      "metadata": {
        "language": "markdown",
        "id": "2effc042-bbe5-4957-8817-4a71a4afeac0"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "fcf7f277-0f11-46a6-b2e1-30e7c5cd7c0c",
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "IO.print(\n        twoPointerStream(nums)\n                .map(pair -> Math.abs(nums[pair[0]]) < Math.abs(nums[pair[1]]) ? \n                        nums[pair[1]] * nums[pair[1]] : nums[pair[0]] * nums[pair[0]])\n                .toList()\n                .reversed()\n        );",
